extends layout

block scripts
  script(src='/javascripts/generation.js')

block content
  div.row.well
    div.span11
      h1(style="text-align:center") Bootstrap your next Android Application
    div.span7
      img(src='/images/ab-screenshot.png')
    
    div.span4
      div
        div.g-plusone
        a.twitter-share-button(href="https://twitter.com/share", data-text="Bootstrap your Android App with Android Bootstrap", data-url="https://www.androidbootstrap.com", data-via="donnfelker", data-lang="en") Tweet
      
      p Android Bootstrap includes a full working implementation of Fragments, Fragment Pager, Account Manager, <a href='https://github.com/jayway/maven-android-plugin'>android-maven-plugin</a>, <a href='https://github.com/square/dagger'>Dagger</a>, <a href="http://www.actionbarsherlock.com">ActionBarSherlock 4</a>, <a href="https://github.com/SimonVT/android-menudrawer">Menu Drawer</a>, <a href='http://viewpagerindicator.com/'>ViewPagerIndicator</a>, <a href="https://github.com/kevinsawicki/http-request">http-request</a>, <a href='http://code.google.com/p/google-gson/'>GSON</a>, <a href='http://code.google.com/p/robotium/'>Robotium</a> for integration testing, API Consumption with an API on <a href='http://www.parse.com'>Parse.com</a> and much more.

      div
        h3 Get Started Now
        h5 Download the Source
        a(href='http://www.github.com/donnfelker/android-bootstrap') Download from GitHub
        br
        a(href='http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YbyzRNxcvZw&feature=youtube_gdata') Watch the How To Video
        h5 or
        h5 Generate Your App Now
      div
        input(id='appName', type='text', placeholder="Your App Name")
        input(id='packageName', type='text', placeholder="com.yourapp.package.name")    

      div
        input(type='submit', value='Generate Your App', id='generate-app', class='btn btn-primary btn-large')

      div.alert.alert-error.alert-block(style="margin-top:10px")
         <b>Note:</b> Currently application generation is <i>very beta</i>. <a href="https://github.com/donnfelker/android-bootstrap-site/issues">Report an issue</a>

      div
        h3 Questions? 
        a(href='https://groups.google.com/forum/#!forum/android-bootstrap') Visit the Android Bootstrap Google Group

  div.row
    div.span4
        h4 Why was this developed? 
        p Building an application without Android Bootstrap could easily take 1-3 weeks of developing, debugging and hacking (depending on your experience level with the Standard Android Developer tools). Android Bootstrap and its app generator eliminate the need for most of this work, freeing your valuable time for making great apps.
    div.span4 
        h4 What does app generation do?
        p The app generation process does a brute force replace through the android-bootstrap source code and replaces build artifact names, package names and imports. It also generates the proper file structure for your package and updates account manager settings as well as build settings.
    div.span4
        h4 Why should I generate my app? 
        p Because its AWEEEESSSOMMMMMEEEE!!!!! No, really, it is. Using the generator you can shave weeks of development, debugging and rid yourself of the continual face-palming that occurs during the highly error prone manual renaming process. 